  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our Discord-  </h1><p> - <br><br><i>*Wild Legion es parte de Erabit's Bud Scheme, un espacio para la creatividad de juegos y desarrolladores en solitario/equipos pequeños para prosperar.</i><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Wilderness Calls!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Embark on an epic adventure in the wilderness, where you'll brandish an arsenal of unique weapons, clash with hordes of formidable enemies, and amass precious materials and gold coins.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/8d03e1bb4e564a1059a0d780b98d61be.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0c49e765b0926b71b9d13d3e42bdce49.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0c49e765b0926b71b9d13d3e42bdce49.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0c49e765b0926b71b9d13d3e42bdce49.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Gather</strong> wood to <strong>Build</strong> mighty <strong>Towers</strong> that will serve as your last line of defense. Use more wood to upgrade or repair towers. Or craft many bombs to BOOM enemies out of existence<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/92cea5feea3c369009c2ab2b3f569a5d.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/6cad8270e19377131cbf205aa4986bca.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=660 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/6cad8270e19377131cbf205aa4986bca.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/6cad8270e19377131cbf205aa4986bca.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Gold coins = EXP</strong>. <br><strong>Kill enemies</strong> to <strong>get coins</strong> to <strong>level up</strong> and buy stats, weapons, or buffs. Wield <strong>multiple weapons</strong> — melee, ranged, and magic. Upgrade weapons and spells to MAX and buy related BUFF to unlock S-Rank synergies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/7a4a5e458d2b237da595f5d3247b3439.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/3d194aa0d5b36b3327e8f186f76d2c91.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather resources by <strong>DAY</strong>, when orcs target you. Protect the Moon Tower by <strong>NIGHT</strong> from the 4-side siege. During the day more resources appear, and orcs only target you. But during the night when the Moon Tower rises, orcs attack it and you need to <strong>build protective towers</strong> around it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/69f0defbf0b65d170001cc852075435e.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/b28451d02073c194bcc753648a32e90e.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Take the lost animal running in circles to the teleport</strong> to escape the orc invasion. In return, <strong>they will grant you special gifts</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/0b610529fc80b35460b994abb3e5c85e.avif?t=1763424459\" width=400 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/7a80003210e51d1c61e90157d260a2a4.poster.avif?t=1763424459\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/7a80003210e51d1c61e90157d260a2a4.webm?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359760/extras/7a80003210e51d1c61e90157d260a2a4.mp4?t=1763424459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kill Bosses and elites to get a chance to receive gems. Then spend gems to increase your stats OR buy new towers.<br><br><i>We took big inspiration from Brotato, Noobs want to live, and Don't Starve. If you like the results of our efforts, please wishlist the game!</i><br> - <br><br><i>*Wild Legion es parte de Erabit's Bud Scheme, un espacio para la creatividad de juegos y desarrolladores en solitario/equipos pequeños para prosperar.</i><br>",
